description.narrative: This activity (PHASE Monitoring and Surge Staff) is a component of Providing Humanitarian Assistance in Sahel Emergencies (PHASE) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £3,081,235. This component benefits South of Sahara, regional, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: CANADEM, Crown Agents Limited, Danish Refugee Council, Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office, Norwegian Refugee Council, Palladium International Ltd (UK), RedR. The start date is 01-11-2014 and the end date is 19-11-2019.
